  # Get Lab Tests by Category
  
  Filter lab tests by medical category/specialty.
  
  ## Common Lab Categories
  - **Hematology**: Blood cell counts (CBC, etc.)
  - **Chemistry**: Metabolic panels, liver/kidney function
  - **Lipid Profile**: Cholesterol and triglycerides
  - **Endocrinology**: Hormone tests
  - **Immunology**: Immune system tests
  - **Microbiology**: Infection/culture tests
  
  ## Use Case
  View all blood count tests for monitoring during treatment.
}
